OL,7,FA motorcycle instructor died after
OL,8,Ffalling off his bike and being hit by
OL,9,Fa fellow rider on a track day in
OL,10,FPortugal, an inquest has heard.
OL,12,FDaniel Maher-Wood, from Crowle in
OL,13,Fnorthern Lincolnshire, was on a lap of
OL,14,Fthe Frequesia de Avalade track at
OL,15,FConcelho de Lisboa, Portugal, when he
OL,16,Fsuffered fatal injuries in June 2022.
OL,18,FThe 29-year-old was among 15 riders on
OL,19,Fa "sighting lap" before a 20-minute
OL,20,Friding session, the inquest at Grimsby
OL,21,FTown Hall was told.
