OL,5,CPortugal
OL,7,FHis father, Martin Maher, who was at
OL,8,Fthe track at the time, told the
OL,9,Finquest of his shock after his son
OL,10,Ffailed to appear as he stood in the
OL,11,Fpits waiting to take a photograph of
OL,12,Fhim.
OL,14,F"I knew something was amiss. Then the
OL,15,Fred lights came on. I was still
OL,16,Fexpecting him to come into the pits,"
OL,17,Fhe said.
OL,19,FMr Maher said He said the collision
OL,20,Fwas the result of "a very novice
OL,21,Ferror".
