OL,7,FHe added: "On a sighting lap you are
OL,8,Fnot allowed to overtake. There are
OL,9,Fthings I don't know that can't be
OL,10,Fanswered."JHe added: "Was it
OL,11,Favoidable? 100% it was avoidable."
OL,13,FHe paid tribute to his son saying he
OL,14,Fwas "a big, strong and fit lad" and "a
OL,15,Flovely young man.
OL,17,FSenior coroner, Paul Smith recorded a
OL,18,Fverdict of accidental death.
